<subSubSection id="E29E3126FE8AF0185B95B293487F6538" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="449038B428EF1E0DC4A508D549B7CDA5" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="88332D1CFDC28A4FBD31E869DC896359" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Referring to the pubescence of hypandrium on the portion fused to paramere in the new species.</paragraph>
